data.description: New - Price Improvement!  Adorable single story home with tranquil backyard setting awaits its new owner! Enter into a welcoming front sitting porch & into your home which boasts 1,740 square feet of living space, vaulted ceilings, 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, stylish kitchen with granite counters & stainless steel appliances, formal living room & separate family room give additional living space for relaxation & gatherings. A spacious & private primary suite with walk-in closet includes a generous primary bath with double sinks. Easy to maintain laminate & tile flooring throughout, dual pane windows & air conditioning. Large 7,701 square foot backyard offers mature trees, storage shed with built-ins & electricity, patio area with stone pavers ideal for outdoor dining & entertaining. Located near Summer Drive neighborhood park with access to the new walking/biking trail. This property is centrally located to Hollister High School, shopping & restaurants. Embrace the Hollister lifestyle today!
